draft.title: SMARTYPANTS Funny Christmas Jumper Sweatshirt - Rude Adult Humour My Second Favourite C Word Slogan - Novelty Xmas Gift For Men Women - Secret Santa Present For Him/Her - Unisex
draft.description:
Tired of the same old sentimental Christmas jumpers? Make a bold statement this festive season with the 'Second Favourite C Word' sweatshirt from SMARTYPANTS. This design is perfect for those who appreciate sharp wit and adult humour and is guaranteed to be the talk of any Christmas party or family gathering.

Crafted from a wonderfully soft and comfortable cotton blend, this pullover isn't just about the laughs – it's about all-day comfort and warmth. The high-quality, durable print on both the front and back ensures the joke won't fade away after a few washes. Whether you're looking for a hilarious Secret Santa gift, a standout piece for the office party, or just a cosy top for a festive night in, this sweatshirt delivers on both style and substance.

bullets: Cheeky Christmas Humour – Guaranteed to raise a smile this festive season this jumper features a hilarious sweary slogan perfect for office parties or as a Secret Santa gift.
Premium Cosy Fabric – Expertly crafted from a soft and durable cotton blend this sweatshirt provides ultimate comfort and warmth throughout the chilly winter months.
Everyday Practical Wear – Designed for convenience this easy-care pullover is fully machine washable and built to last making it a practical and stylish choice for casual wear.
Vibrant Dual-Sided Print – Featuring a high-quality print on both the front and back the design's crisp white text and festive details are made to resist fading wash after wash.
The Perfect Novelty Gift – An ideal present for friends family or colleagues with a great sense of humour this top is perfect for Christmas Jumper Day pub trips or festive lounging.
